column4: Awalnya mahluk ini dibuat dengan niat yang baik,namun saat ini para golem digerakkan karena pengaruh kekuatan jahat.

column2: A lesser demon summoned by its demonic superiors to invade towers.
column3: 탑의 공략을 위해 마족들이 마계에서 차출한 하위마족입니다.
column4: Kaum demon tingkat lemah yang disummon oleh demon yang lebih kuat untuk menyerang tower.

column2: These lesser demons come in countless types due to their populous numbers.
column3: 하급 마족으로 마계에는 이들이 수를 셀 수 없을 정도로 많고 종류도 다양하다고 합니다.
column4: Kaum demon tingkat lemah yang tidak terhitung jumlahnya dan memiliki banyak jenis.

column2: This species was once fairly rare; however, in recent times, their numbers have greatly increased.
column3: 이들은 원래 희귀한 생물이었으나 근래 숫자가 늘어났습니다.
column4: Mereka awalnya adalah species langka, namun jumlahnya meningkat akhir-akhir ini.

column2: The Big Cockatrice is quite dangerous, as its glare and breath can petrify any opponent. Engaging this creature should not be taken lightly.
column3: 대형 코카트리스입니다. 위험성, 특히 석화위험성은 아무리 강조해도 지나치지 않습니다.
column4: Merupakan Cockatries berukuran besar. Sangat berbahaya, terutama serangannya yang sangat mematikan.

column2: The number of Bagworms is no longer increasing, yet its current population is enough not to worry about extinction.
column3: 누덕고치는 더 이상 발생하지는 않지만, 현재 개체수만으로도 멸종을 걱정할 필요가 없는 몬스터입니다.
column4: Bagworm tidak bertambah lagi jumlahnya,tetapi melihat populasinya yang ada sekarang ini maka tidak perlu khawatir ia akan punah.

column2: Its body vanishes if you stay away from it for a long time.
column3: 본체에서 오랜 시간 멀어지면 자연히 소멸됩니다.
column4: Jika meninggalkan tubuh aslinya dalam waktu yang lama, maka akan hancur secara alami.

column2: It used its hook on a large monster to come over from the demon realm, and has underwent a lot of change.
column3: 큰 몬스터에게 갈고리를 사용하여 붙어서 마계로부터 넘어온 후 많은 변화를 한 몬스터입니다.
column4: Monster yang mengalami banyak perubahan, setelah datang  menempel dengan hooknya pada monster besar dari dunia iblis.

column2: Even though there are less logging activities, the monsters that originated from the stumps continue to show up. They appear to be formed out of the residues of Plant-type monsters.
column3: 벌목이 줄었어도 그루터기에서 기인한 이 몬스터는 계속 생깁니다. 수목형 몬스터의 잔재에서 생성이 목격됩니다.
column4: Meskipun penebangan sudah berkurang, Monster ini tetap bermunculan. Dan dia terbentuk oleh karena sisa-sisa potongan pohon besar.
Time bomb (Hanya untuk di score dungeon)

column2: A popular theory is that you have to be a demon to use this messenger.
column4: Menurut cerita, dahulu kala para Demon menggunakannya sebagai pengirim pesan.
Vubbe yang sering terlihat oleh para manusia.

column2: Over time these Vubbes have become diverse and distinguishable.
column3: 지난 몇 년간 부베 사회는 시간이 지날수록 급격히 분화되고 복잡해져 왔습니다.
column4: Selama bertahun-tahun dalam linkungan sosial Vubbes telah berubah secara cepat dan sangat berbeda, dan menjadi rumit.

column2: It is hard to determine whether their mining roles are permanent since little is known about the Vubbes' social system.
column3: 채굴하는 모습이 많이 목격되어 붙은 이름이지만, 부베 집단의 체계는 명확히 알려지지 않았기에 이들의 역할이 고정적인지는 모릅니다.
column4: Nama yang sering diberikan mereka karena sering terlihat bertambang, tapi karena kehidupan Vubbe tidak diketahui dengan jelas, maka kita tidak tahu apa tugas utama mereka.

column2: Vubbe Archers specialize in using ranged weapons. Thus some people claim the Vubbes have specific roles.
column3: 부베궁수는 투사무기에 특화된 모습을 보입니다. 혹자는 이런 점을 들어 부베의 직군이 명확히 짜져있다고 주장합니다.
column4: Vubbe Archers adalah ahli menggunakan senjata jarak jauh. Inilah yang membuat beberapa orang berpikir vubbe memiliki tugas masing-masing.

column2: It is possible to collect and use the bows and arrows that the Vubbes made.
column3: 부베들이 만든 활과 화살을 수거해서 사용하는 일도 가능하긴 합니다.
column4: Dengan mengumpulkan dan menggunakan busur dan panah yang dibuat Vubbes, mungkin akan ada kesempatan untuk menggunakannya nanti.

column2: A shrub monster that attacks by either firing its twigs or striking with its branches.
column3: 관목이 잔가지를 버리고  두 개의 가지를 사용하여 공격하는 형태로 변이된 몬스터입니다.
column4: Monster yang bermutasi dari semak dan ranting dan memiliki dua tipe serangan.

column2: According to legend this watchdog is a creation that Zachariel the Great had planned to preserve.
column3: 일설에 의하면 경비견은 자카리엘 대왕이 손수 시안을 잡아 만든 것이라 합니다.
column4: Dalam sebuah cerita, Mereka adalah yang pasukan penjaga yang dibuat langsung oleh Raja Zachariel.

column2: Due to its cute appearance many people have tried to win over Tini's heart, but none were successful.
column3: 귀여운 외모 덕에 많은 사람들이 티니를 길들이려 하였으나 성공한 적이 없다고합니다.
column4: Memiliki tampilan yang lucu, sehingga banyak orang telah mengincar Tiny, tapi tidak berhasil.

column2: Tree Ambulo is different from the typical monsters that originated from the demon realm as it is not a deformity between creatures and things.
column3: 트리암불로는 마계에 기원한 몬스터로 선입견과 달리 생물이나 사물이 변형된 몬스터가 아닙니다.
column4: Yang membedakan TreeAmbulo dengan monster lain dari dunia iblis adalah, ia bukan monster yang telah berubah dari mahluk hidup atau benda mati.

column2: It's well-trained to follow its owner's every command. Unfortunately, its owner is usually a demon.
column3: 잘 훈련시키면 주인을 따릅니다. 문제는 그 주인이란 대개 마족이란 점입니다.
column4: Jika melatihnya dengan baik maka akan mengikuti perintah tuannya. Biasanya yang menjadi tuannya adalah kaum Demon.

column2: Shredded is a demon monster that was derived from the by-product that results when you transform a monster into a powerful ghost.
column3: 쉬레디드는 마족이 강력한 원혼으로 몬스터를 만들 때 떨어져 나온 부산물에서 기원한 몬스터입니다.
column4: Shredded adalah Monster yang terbentuk dari sisa-sisa ketika Kaum Demon menciptakan Monster sebagai hantu yang kuat.

column2: Yekub unleashes its infamous cry in the demon realm, which produces many minions and spreads them around the world. Yekubite is the name given to these minions.
column3: 예쿱은 마계에서 악명를 떨친 존재이며 많은 분신을 낳아 세상에 퍼뜨렸습니다. 에큐바이트는 그런 분신들에게 붙여진 이름입니다.
column4: Yekub adalah jiwa dari dunia demon menyebar ke seluruh penjuru untuk membuat kekacauan. Nama Yekubite diberikan kepada Alter Ego mereka.

column2: A possessed demonic monster obsessed with the divine Goddess Statues.
column3: 신성이 떠난 여신상에 빙의한 마족이 자신만의 피조물로 만든 몬스터입니다.
column4: Monster yang terbentuk karena kaum Demon merasuki patung Goddess  yang telah hilang kesuciannya.

column2: This monster does not seem to transmute from typical plants but rather from rotten flora. However, there are no evidence to support this conclusion.
column3: 정확히는 초목이 변형된 몬스터가 아니라 썩어가는 초목이 생명을 얻은 것이라 합니다만, 그 흔적은 찾기 쉽지 않습니다.
column4: Monster ini tidak berasal dari tanaman biasa, melainkan dari tanaman mati yang diberikan kehidupan, tapi tidak ada teori yang bisa membuktikannya.

column2: Upon transforming into a monster with a hardened wood body and no leaves, Treegool supplants its former photosynthetic diet with hunting.
column3: 몬스터로 변한 후 목질이 단단해지고 잎이 없어진 트리굴은 없어진 광합성 능력을 사냥으로 보충합니다.
column4: Setelah menjadi monster, dengan badan kayu yang keras dan tidak memiliki daun. Treegol mencari makan dengan berburu.

column2: Existing since ancient times, Ammon has harmed countless people and monsters.
column3: 암몬은 고대부터 존재한 몬스터로 많은 사람을 해쳐왔습니다.
column4: Ammon telah membahayakan manusia sejak lama, ia adalah monster dari zaman kuno

column2: While it has maintained its original form, Operor has developed severely aggressive and violent behavior.
column3: 오페러는 비교적 원형을 유지하고 있는 몬스터지만, 그 공격성과 사나움은 심해졌습니다.
column4: Operor adalah monster jenis yang tetap menjaga bentuk aslinya, suka menyerang dan sangat kejam.

column2: A severely mutated bee and beetle hybrid with qualities of both, it operates in swarms.
column3: 벌과 딱정벌레의 장점에 변이된 몬스터의 사나움이 깃든 몬스터입니다. 벌처럼 체계를 지닙니다.
column4: Monster mutasi dari lebah dan kumbang yang buas. Memiliki sistem pertahanan seperti armor

column2: Before it was revealed to be a mutated plant, it was speculated to be a monster's larva.
column3: 식물변형이란 점이 밝혀지기 전에는 어떤 몬스터의 유충이 아닌가 추측이 있었습니다.
column4: Sebelum diketahui sebagai perubahan dari tanaman, ia diperkirakan sebagai larva dari suatu Monster yang terbentuk dari mutasi suatu tanaman dan beberapa monster larva.

column2: Animals living in the Royal Mausoleum have been deformed in recent years by the influence of the evil energy.
column3: 왕릉에 서식하던 동물이 근래에 마기의 영향을 받아 변형된 몬스터입니다.
column4: Monster yang awalnya adalah hewan yang hidup di sekitar kuburan raja, dan bermutasi karena mendapatkan pengaruh energi iblis.

column2: It is a magic creature whose name comes from the wishes of a golem species.
column3: 엄밀히는 골렘의 일종이나 만든이의 염원이 담긴 이름을 지닌 마법피조물입니다.
column4: Makhluk yang terbuat dari sihir dan memyimpan kekuatan golem tertentu yang garang.

column2: A magical creature created to protect the Royal Mausoleum. Despite being weak, it is strong enough to resist the goddess' powers.
column3: 왕릉을 수호하기 위해 만들어진 마법피조물이며 약하지만 여신의 힘도 깃들어 마족에게 강한 편입니다.
column4: Makhluk penunggu makam raja, Walaupun lemah namun memiliki kekuatan Goddess dan termasuk kuat bagi kaum Demon.

column2: Despite its appearance, this magical creation has received the blessing of the goddess. Can deal critical damage to demons.
column3: 외양과 달리 이 마법피조물에는 여신의 축복이 깃들어 있어 마족에게 치명적일 수 있습니다.
column4: Tidak seperti penampilannya, kekuatannya yang diberikan oleh Goddess  dapat berpengaruh fatal ke Demon.

column2: Many creatures have been placed in the Royal Mausoleum, including the Tombsinker, to guard against intruding demons.
column3: 툼싱커를 비롯한 왕릉에 배치된 것들은 특별히 마족의 침입에 강하도록 만들어졌습니다.
column4: Tombsinker dibuat dan ditempatkan di Makam raja dengan tujuan untuk mengganggu aktivitas Demon yang menyusup.

column2: There are rumors saying the Weaver is looking for thread made of stone.
column3: 위버가 돌로 된 실을 잣는다는 소문이 있습니다.
column4: Benang weaver terbuat dari bahan yang kuat sekeras batu

column2: Please do not look directly into their hoods.
column3: 그들 머리 부분의 깊은 공허를 직시하지 마십시오.
column4: Jangan ruang kosong secara langsung yang merupakan bagian kepala mereka.

column2: Firm and toxic, their blood-sucking ability is unique.
column3: 단단하고 독성이 있으며 무엇보다 흡혈 본능이 남아 있습니다.
column4: Keras dan memiliki racun dan suka menghisap darah.

column2: Unlike traditional Golems, Zolem move by a mysterious aura, not magic.
column3: 졸렘이 일반 골렘과 다른 차이점은 마법이 아닌 다른 기운에 의해 움직인다는 점입니다.
column4: Zolem berbeda dari golem biasa yang bergerak karena magic, dia digerakkan oleh aura.

column2: Although a Kepa by name, it actually comes from the demon realm.
column3: 케파가 연상되어 명칭이 붙었지만, 엄연히 마계를 기원으로 하는 몬스터입니다.
column4: Masih keturunan dari kepa, monster asli yang berasal dari dunia iblis.

column2: An evil goblin summoned by the Vubbes. It sometimes appear even in areas where Vubbes are not found.
column3: 부베가 마족의 사주를 받아 불러낸 마물의 일종입니다. 경로는 모르지만 부베가 활동하지 않는 지역에서도 나타나곤 합니다.
column4: Makhluk jahat yang dipanggil Vubbes karena menerima takdirnya dari Kaum demon. Walaupun tidak diketahui lokasi jelasnya, sesekali ia muncul di luar area aktivitas Vubbes.

column2: A mutant monster that looks like a dolphin. Its other features correspond to a small Stone Whale.
column3: 변이형 몬스터가 돌고래라는 특정한 형태를 갖춰 그에 맞는 특성을 보이는 흔치 않은 특징의 몬스터입니다. 석화고래의 소형에 해당합니다.
column4: Sering dianggap sebagai lumba-lumba karena karakteristiknya yang mirip. namun sebenarnya monster mutasi yang berasal dari Stone Whale.

column2: Although a clyra type because of its sharp tail, this monster seems to have transformed from a pumpkin.
column3: 날카로운 꼬리 때문에 클라이라 종류로 여겨졌지만 호박성 광물을 기원으로 변형된 몬스터로 보입니다.
column4: Dianggap sebagai Monster tipe Clay karena memiliki ekor yang tajam, dan terlihat seperti monster evolusi yang terbuat dari batu amber tambang.

column2: As demons become more populous, new varieties of them appear. Infroholder is one of these new types of demon.
column3: 마족이 출현이 빈번해지자 그로부터 많은 변종이 생겼는데, 인프로홀더 역시 그런 몬스터의 하나입니다.
column4: Walau banyak memiliki sub-spesies yang banyak dari Demon. Infroholder menjadi salah satu yang sering muncul.

column2: In the past this animal was quite friendly towards humans, but now it's even more dangerous than a bear.
column3: 한때는 인간에게 친숙한 동물이었지만, 지금은 곰보다 위험한 생물입니다.
column4: Dahulu kala merupakan hewan yang jinak terhadap manusia, namun sekarang lebih ganas dan berbahaya daripada beruang.

column2: The Armori are dullahans whose armors are stained by evil energy.
column3: 아모리는 갑옷이 악한 기운에 물든 것으로 듀라한과는 차이가 있습니다.
column4: Amori adalah sesuatu yang armor nya diselimuti oleh aura kegelapan, ia berbeda dengan Durahan.

column2: Is that another tail hanging on its back?
column3: 대체 저것을 등에 달린 꼬리라고 해야 할까요?
column4: Apakah itu disebut ekor di belakang punggung?

column2: A demon that respects the strong and is cruel to the weak. Nonetheless, its aggression trivializes this characteristic.
column3: 마족치고는 강자를 존경하는 특징이 있습니다. 약자에겐 잔혹하고 강자에겐 더 적극적으로 공격하니 결국 별 차이는 없습니다.
column4: Sebagai Demon sudah seharusnya menghormati yang lebih kuat. Bengis kepada yang lemah, menyerang lebih aggresif.

column2: It is uncertain which monster Infroburk resembles, but it certainly is ferocious.
column3: 인프로버크가 어떤 몬스터의 소형인지 확실하지 않습니다. 확실한 점은 사납다는 것입니다.
column4: InfroBurk monster yang tidak banyak diketahui, namun yang pasti monster ini sangat buas.

column2: They kill their fellow demons out of boredom.
column3: 심심하면 같은 마족 병사도 살해하는 자들입니다.
column4: Ketika bosan, dia juga menghabisi sesamanya Demon.

column2: A small monster that is part turtle and part mineral. It prefers living in solitude rather than in a group.
column3: 거북과 광물이 변이결합한 몬스터의 작은 종류입니다. 모여있어도 동족간의 유대없이 독자적으로 활동합니다.
column4: Termasuk monster kecil yang merupakan campuran mutasi akan barang tambang dan kura-kura. Walaupun berkumpul diantara sesamanya, mereka beraktifitas masing-masing tanpa ikatan.

column2: Because of its appearance, novice miners often try to mine the crystal on the spider's back and are attacked.
column3: 외형때문에 가끔씩 초보광부들이 거미 등의 수정을 캐려고 하다가 공격을 당하곤 했습니다.
column4: Karena tampilan luarnya, terkadang para penambang pemula bermaksud mengambil kristal dari punggung laba-laba, dan mendapat serangan darinya.

column2: Those who see Filibo as a small and cute critter will quickly be injured by it.
column3: 처음 출현 당시 작고 귀엽다고 생각한 사람들이 많이 피해를 입었습니다.
column4: Banyak orang yang telah terluka olehnya karena menanggapnya kecil dan lucu pada saat pertama kali melihatnya.

column2: Acting as Mirtis' scout minion, these bats once lived throughout the world but have grown into a large threat despite of their small bodies.
column3: 미르티스가 정찰을 위해 세계 곳곳에 퍼뜨린 박쥐는 이제 본체와 상관없이 증식하며 위협이 되고 있습니다.
column4: Kelelawar yang menyebar di seluruh penjuru dunia kini telah tumbuh menjadi berbahaya dan menjadi ancaman.

column2: Although the Hogmas are smarter than the Vubbes and can use tools, their brutish instincts stifle any progress and lead to many stupid mistakes.
column3: 호그마는 부베보다 높은 지능을 지녀 도구를 사용하지만, 너무 강한 본능탓에 어리석은 실수를 하곤 하며 진보에는 무딥니다.
column4: Hogma lebih pintar daripada Vubbes dalam menggunakan peralatan, tetapi instingnya yang kuat membuat mereka sering melakukan kesalahan bodoh.

column2: Levelheaded Hogmas are often seen taking the role of archers.
column3: 절제력을 지닌 호그마들이 궁수역할을 담당하곤 합니다.
column4: Para Hogma yang memiliki disiplin baik, berperan sebagai pasukan penembak

column2: Some Hogmas have picked up abilities through experience but they still have Hogma instincts.
column3: 호그마중에 경험을 통해 능력을 지닌 자가 있습니다. 다만 주술사도 호그마의 본능에서 자유롭진 않습니다.
column4: Beberapa dari mereka memiliki pengalaman dalam menghadapi Hogg. Hanya saja sebagai Shaman, Hogma tidaklah memiliki insting yang leluasa.

column2: It is said that they receive their powers from human souls because they gather toward the injured.
column3: 부상자에게 모여드는 습성때문에 엘롬은 인간의 영혼에서 힘을 얻는다고 전해집니다.
column4: Ellom memiliki kebiasaan menyerang secara bersamaan, dikatakan bahwa mereka mendapat kekuatan dari jiwa manusia.

column2: This type of Ellom is toxic.
Merog variant. Slight differences in the mutation process differentiates the variety of Merogs.
column3: 메로그의 변종입니다. 메로그들의 차이는 단순한 변이 과정의 차이에서 기인한 것으로 추측됩니다.
column4: Jenis lain dari Merlog. Hanya saja ia berubah dan memiliki sedikit perbedaan dari sebelumnya.

column2: This reptile monster attacks instinctively but shows as much abilities as its intelligence.
column3: 본능적으로 공격하지만, 지능에 못지 않은 능력을 보여주는 파충류 변이 몬스터입니다.
column4: Memiliki insting menyerang, tetapi merupakan monster mutasi dari reptil yang memiliki insting kurang baik.

column2: A Hogma whose intelligence and instinct give them leadership in the fight against humans.
column3: 호그마 중에 지능과 본능을 적절히 다둘줄 알면 무리의 지휘자로 인정되며 주로 인간과의 전투에서 활약하게 됩니다.
column4: Diantara Hogma, ia memiliki insting dan kecerdasan yang baik dan menjadi pemimpin dalam kelompok. Ia juga aktif dalam menyerang manusia dalam pertempuran.

column2: A monster which is said to be created by demons using the Chupacabra.
column3: 마족이 츄파카브라를 이용해 만들어 낸 몬스터로 추측되고 있습니다.
column4: Monster yang diketahui, dibuat oleh para Demon dengan menggunakan Chupacabra.

column2: It is both filthy in nature and surly in its appearance.
column4: Memiliki kebiasaan yang kotor seperti penampilannya.

column2: It is fierce against other monsters and humans, more so especially with Insect-type monsters.
column3: 다른 몬스터 특히 곤충형 몬스터에게도 사납습니다. 사람은 말할 것도 없습니다.
column4: Monster yang buas terhadap monster lain, terutama terhadap tipe serangga. Tidak ada yang perlu dibicarakan mengenai manusia.

column2: Amphibians that have branched out and evolved to be able to hunt in arid areas, travelers should be wary of them.
column3: 양서류가 원형이지만, 물이 없는 곳에서도 사냥이 가능한 몬스터로 변이한 후 여행자들의 위험이 된 몬스터입니다.
column4: Memiliki bentuk asli amfibi, tetapi telah bermutasi menjadi monster yang dapat berburu di tempat tak berair, dan menjadi ancaman pagi para penjelajah.

column2: A monster with a habit of baiting and attacking humans.
column3: 사람을 습격해 먹이로 삼는 포악한 습성을 지닌 몬스터입니다.
column4: Monster yang memiliki kebiasaan jahat, yaitu menyerang dan memangsa orang.

column2: You can tell the origin of this beast just by its name or appearance.
column3: 외양과 이름에서 그 연원을 쉽게 알 수 있는 야수 몬스터입니다.
column4: Dari nama dan penampilannya, sangat mudah melihat bahwa monster ini buas.

column2: Tama is a monster originating from the spores of some plants. It is unclear whether it will still grow from its current form.
column3: 타마 역시 어떤 식물의 포자에서 기원한 몬스터입니다. 지금 형태에서 다르게 성장하는지는 확실치 않습니다.
column4: Tama monster yang berasal dari spora suatu tanaman . Tidak jelas bagaimana dia hidup dengan tubuh yang seperti itu.

column2: Kepari are not related with the Kepa, and are instead akin to animals.
column3: 케파와는 관련이 없습니다. 이들은 동물에 속합니다.
column4: Monster ini tidak ada hubungan dengan Kepa. Monster ini berasal dari suatu hewan

column2: Since the disappearance of the goddesses, one of the most bizarre change is that these water-dwelling creatures are now active on land.
column3: 여신들께서 자취를 감추신 후 가장 이색적인 변화의 하나는 물속 생물이 뭍에서 활동하는 일입니다.
column4: Setelah Goddess hilang, ia menjadi salah satu monster aneh yang aktif di darat.

column2: It still tends to gravitate toward rotten flesh.
column3: 썩은 고기를 노리던 습성은 여전히 남아 있습니다.
column4: Kebiasaan buruknya dalam mengincar daging busuk masih tetap ada.

column2: It is not yet clear what deforms into this monster.
column3: 어떤 무생물이 변형된 몬스터인지 아직 밝혀지지 않았습니다.
column4: Tidak diketahui jelas dari makhluk apakah dia berasal.

column2: Similar to the Lemur, but cold-resistant.
column4: Mirip seperti Lemur, sangat kuat di udara dingin.

column2: While they look like guardsmen, these Hogmas have extensive battle experience.
column3: 파수꾼과 유사해보일뿐 실은 훨씬 많은 전투경험을 지닌 호그마입니다.
column4: Hogma yang memiliki pengalaman bertarung yang lebih banyak, walaupun terlihat sama dengan Scout.

column2: Compared to an average Hogmas, they are very stronger, but their intelligence is lower.
column3: 선입견과 달리 이들운 힘은 세지만, 가장 지능이 낮은 호그마입니다.
column4: Merupakan Hogma dengan tingkat kecerdasan paling rendah dibandingkan yang lainnya, walaupun memiliki kekuatan besar.

column2: It is a monster that is formed by binding an animal with a mineral. In recent years, various forms of these monsters have been discovered.
column3: 동물과 광물이 결합한 몬스터이며 최근에 이 몬스터의 다양한 변형이 발견되고 있습니다.
column4: Monster ini berasal dari gabungan hewan dan mineral, berbagai jenis mutasi lain dari monster ini telah ditemukan belakangan.

column2: It is one of several variations of Zinute.
A variety of Chupacabra dwell in various places, causing harm to both human life and crops.
column3: 츄파카브라는 다양한 종류가 곳곳에 동시다발적으로 출몰하여 인명과 작물을 해치고 있습니다.
column4: Chupacabra memiliki banyak jenis dan muncul secara serentak di beberapa tempat, lalu melukai manusia dan hasil pertanian di sekitar.

column2: Although small, it has grown bigger than its original state and hunts for meat throughout its life
column3: 작지만 본래보다 커진 바브는 끝없이 생명체의 살을 노립니다.
column4: Menjadi lebih besar daripada aslinya dan mengincar daging mahluk hidup untuk bertahan hidup.

column2: While it has no eyes, Arma has a highly developed sense of hearing and smell.
column3: 눈은 없지만 청각과 후각이 매우 발달하여 보기보다 민첩합니다.
column4: Tidak memiliki mata, namun dapat mendeteksi dengan pendengaran dan penciuman yang hebat.

column2: It attacks people with a flame ball that it cherishes and carries around.
column3: 항상 애지중지 들고다니는 화염구슬로 사람들을 공격합니다.
column4: Selalu berkeliling dengan membawa bola api yang terlihat disayangi dan menyerang orang menggunakannya.

column2: A monster variant that comes from a wizard's belongings. It is resistive to its original use.
column3: 마법사들의 물품이 변형된 변이형 몬스터입니다. 본래 쓰임에 따른 저항력이 있다고 합니다.
column4: Monster yang bermutasi bentuknya dari peralatan para wizard. Katanya memiliki kekuatan perlawanan tergantung penggunaan awalnya.

column2: A sad monster that can't fly.
column4: Monster sedih karena tidak dapat terbang.

column2: While it was once a creature created by a wizard using the best magic available, it has now turned hostile to humans due to the influence of the demons.
column3: 탑의 마법사들이 이용하던 마법피조물이지만, 현재는 마족의 영향으로 인간에게 적대적으로 변했습니다.
column4: Salah satu mahluk sihir yang dibuat oleh para high wizard, namun bermusuhan dengan manusia akibat pengaruh kaum Demon.

column2: When the demons captured the Mage Tower, this doll was greatly affected. In particular, it instinctively hates magic users.
column3: 마족이 탑을 공략하면서 영향을 받아 몬스터가 되었으며 특히 마법사를 본능적으로 증오합니다.
column4: Ketika kaum Demon menguasai menara, monster ini ikut terpengaruh dan membenci wizard.

column2: The slime is an organism in the demon realm. Its population exploded after the time when the plant Geant, especially around the Mage Tower.
column3: 슬라임은 마계에 속한 생물로 식물제앙의 날 이후 늘어났으며, 특히 마법사의 탑 주위에 많습니다.
column4: Slime makhluk yang berevolusi dari dunia demon, biasanya berada di sekitar Mage Tower.

column2: One of the demon's lower level creature.They possess a little bit of intelligence.
column3: 마계의 하급 생물 가운데 하나입니다. 약간의 지능이 있습니다.
column4: Salah satu makhluk kelas rendah dari dunia Demon. Memiliki sedikit kecerdasan.

column2: When botanists first discovered the Raflower, they planned on naming it Tripede, a name that has since been given to another monster.
column3: 식물학자들은 처음에는 움직이는 라플라스가 발견되면 트리피드란 이름을 붙이려고 했으나 그 명칭은 다른 몬스터에게 부여되었습니다.
column4: Ketika Para ahli botanologis pertama kali menemukan Rafloweer yang dapat bergerak, mereka bermaksud memberikan nama Tripede, tetapi akhirnya nama itu diberikan kepada monster lainnya.

column2: A monster whose habitat has been relocated close to the volcano.
column4: Sebelumnya, Monster ini hidup di sekitar gunung berapi.

column2: A hybrid monster that exhibit the advantages of having the body of two known beasts.
column3: 여러 짐승의 다양하 장점이 한 몸에 있어 까다로운 몬스터입니다.
column4: Monster ganas yang memiliki berbagai kelebihan dari makhluk buas lainnya dalam tubuhnya.

column2: Ultanuns have always been flightless birds even before its deformation.
column4: Ultanun adalah burung yang tidak dapat terbang sejak sebelum bermutasi.

column2: Don't let its cute appearance fool you. This monster will try to tear you apart, given the chance.
column3: 루바보스를 귀엽다고 생각하는 사람도 있지만, 이 몬스터는 언제나 당신을 찢을 준비가 되어 있습니다.
column4: Beberapa orang mengiranya adalah monster yang lucu, namun monster ini selalu siap untuk mencabik-cabik manusia.

column2: A Panto variant with distinctively high intelligence. They often show up with the other Panto variants.
column3: 판토의 또 다른 변이 아종으로 특정한 일에만 지능이 높습니다. 다만 이후 다른 변화를 보일 가능성이 있습니다.
column4: merupakan salah satu subspecies mutasi Panto yang memiliki kepintaran yang tinggi pada pekerjaan tertentu saja. Hanya saja setelah itu, terlihat adanya kemungkinan perubahan lainnya.

column2: The Panto Shaman is powerful, but it does not know were they are in a developing type of wizard. The obvious point is that you must pay more attention to them during combat.
column3: 판토주술사는 강력하지만, 마법사의 발전형인지는 확실하지 않습니다. 분명한 점은 전투에서 더 주의해야 한다는 점입니다.
column4: Panto shaman adalah monster kuat, tetapi tidak diketahui jelas apakah mereka adalah bentuk evolusi wizard atau bukan. Satu hal yang pasti kamu harus lebih berhati-hati padanya ketika pertempuran.

column2: A somewhat cute mutant that is always expressionless. They assemble together when chanting.
column3: 귀엽게 생긴 외모와는 다르게 무표정으로 항상 일관하며 대뜸 몸통박치기를 시전하곤 합니다.
column4: Tidak seperti penampilannya yang lucu, terkadang ia dapat menerjang dengan tiba-tiba.

column2: Moyabu has evolved from the Moya. It is more violent than the Moya.
column4: Hasil evolusi dari Moya, dan menjadi lebih buas.

column2: When it comes to flight, Bavon would be better just floating there as is.
column3: 바본은 비행한다기보다는 부유한다고 하는 편이 맞을 것 같습니다.
column4: Terlihat bodoh karena tidak dapat terbang dan hanya melayang.

column2: A carnivorous plant that uses bait to catch food. It shred its food into pieces before swallowing.
column3: 타누는 먹이를 크게 썰어 삼켜서 섭취하며 식충식물이 식육식물로 변이된 종류입니다.
column4: Tanu merupakan mutasi dari tanaman pemakan serangga menjadi tanaman karnivora yang menggunakan makanan sebagai umpan.

column2: A three headed monster. It is hard to tell whether the main body is just one head or all three.
column3: 머리가 셋 달린 열매 몬스터입니다. 어떤 머리가 본체인지 혹은 모두가 본체인지 알려지지 않았습니다.
column4: Monster yang memiliki 3 kepala, tidak diketahui yang mana kepala aslinya.

column2: This beast that once exclusively roamed in the demon realm. Nowadays it is found all over the world, endangering other wildlife and humans.
column3: 마계의 환경을 누비는 맹수이며 지금은 우리 세상에 건너와 해를 끼치고 있습니다.
column4: Monster yang berasal dari daerah dunia demon,  sekarang ia menyebrang ke dunia kita dan merusak lingkungan.

column2: The demons have tamed Denden and uses it for their means.
column3: 마족들은 덴덴을 길들여 부리려는 작업을 진행중이라 합니다.
column4: Para kaum Demon melatih Denden untuk menyelesaikan suatu pekerjaan tertentu.

column2: If a moving poisonous mushroom makes you anxious, consider Doyor as an example.
column4: Jika kamu penasaran dengan jamur beracun yang dapat bergerak, maka lihatlah Doyor.

column2: The yellow grass on its body looks supple. But if you touch it, it can be quite painful .
column3: 몸 위쪽의 노란 풀은 보들보들해보이지만 맞으면 꽤 아픕니다
column4: Pada bagian tubuhnya terlihat rumput lembut yang berwarna kuning, namun sangat menyakitkan ketika terkena.

column2: The Rondo is not an animal found in our world, rather it is an animal that crossed from the demon realm.
column3: 론도는 우리 세계 동물의 변형이 아닙니다. 마계의 생물이 건너온 것입니다.
column4: Rondo adalah bukan bentuk evolusi dari monster dunia kita, tetapi merupakan mahluk yang datang menyebrang dari dunia demon.

column2: The Terra Imp is quite mischievous. One should be aware of their belongings, as they might steal them.
column3: 장난기가 매우 많아 모험가의 물건에 관심이 많으니 소지품 관리에 주의를 요합니다.
column4: Ia memilik banyak mainan dan tertarik dengan barang para petualang. Berhati-hatilah terhadap barang bawaanmu.

column2: Although it appears to have no sharp edges, it will when engaged in battle.
column3: 별로 날카로운 부분이 없어 보이지만, 실제로 싸워보면 다릅니다.
column4: Terlihat tidak memiliki bagian yang tajam, tetapi berbeda ketika mencoba bertarung sebenarnya.

column2: There are not too many cases of a fruit deformed monsters. Leafnut belongs to these few cases.
column3: 의외로 열매가 변형된 몬스터는 많지 않습니다. 리프넛은 소수 사례에 속합니다.
column4: Tidak banyak Monster dari buah yang perubahannya tak terduga. Leafnut merupakan salah satu dari sebagian kecil itu.

column2: Its elongated pupils are a distinctive feature.
column3: 매력포인트는 일자로 쭉 찢어진 길다란 동공.
column4: Memiliki daya tarik yaitu bola mata yang besar

column2: A Panto with excellent fighting skills and is one of the strongest subspecies in the forest.
column3: 판토 중에 전투력이 높고 숲지형에 강한 아종을 지칭합니다.
column4: Panto yang memiliki kemampuan bertarung yang tinggi.

column2: The flowers around its neck are actually real flowers rather than decorations.
column3: 목 주변의 꽃은 장식이 아니라 진짜 살아있는 꽃입니다.
column4: Bunga yang berada di lehernya adalah bunga asli dan bukan hiasan.

column2: If you carelessly touch the leaves on its head, Mali will unleash its relentless anger towards you.
column3: 머리 위의 잎을 함부로 건드렸다간 말리의 집요한 분노에 시달리게될겁니다.
column4: Jika kamu menyentuh daun di kepalanya secara sembarangan, Mally akan menyerang kamu.

column2: Be aware of the smoke that this creature spurts as it is highly toxic and will last for a while.
column3: 그루머가 뿜어내는 연기는 매우 독성이 강하고 오래가니 주의를 요합니다
column4: Grummer dapat mengeluarkan asap yang sangat beracun dan bertahan lama, maka dari itu harap waspada.

column2: A bite from its sharp beak causes persistent pain, which may last for a while.
column3: 날카로운 침에 쏘이면 한동안 통증이 지속되니 주의하세요.
column4: Hati-hati karena luka akibat terkena durinya sangat menyakitkan.

column2: The edges of its wings are covered in poison. Touching it may cause paralysis.
column3: 뿔에는 독이 없지만 날개에는 마비성분이 있을수도 있으니 되도록 직접 만지지 않도록합니다.
column4: Ia tidak memiliki racun di tanduknya, tetapi mungkin terdapat bubuk paralyze pada sayapnya, sehingga jangan menyentuhnya secara langsung.

column2: A low-ranking demon who is always looking for opportunities to promote itself.
column3: 이들은 마계에서 생각보다 지위가 낮기 때문에 이곳에서 큰 공을 세울 기회를 찾고 있습니다.
column4: Karena mereka memiliki posisi rendahan di dunia Demon, maka mereka sedang mencari peruntungan di tempat ini.

column2: The Seedmia are very troublesome as they are able to shoot seeds over exceptionally long distances.
column3: 씨드미아는 씨앗을 꽤 멀리까지 날려보낼 수 있어서 대단히 성가십니다.
column4: Seedmia sungguh merepotkan karena dia dapat melempar biji cukup jauh.

column2: A moving tree monster that appeared after the Great Plant Cataclysm, it was named after its discoverer.
column3: 초목재앙이 발생한 후 많은 나무가 움직이는 몬스터가 되었으며 피렌트는 최초 발견자의 이름을 따라 명명되었습니다.
column4: Setelah bencana yang menyerang tanaman terjadi maka banyak pohon berubah menjadi monster, nama monster ini diberikan sesuai nama orang yang menemukannya pertama kali.

column2: Galok is a monster who command workers in the demon realm.
column4: Galok adalah monster yang mengawasi para pekerja di dunia Demon.

column2: Upent rapidly appeared from what once were flora with magical powers.
column3: 우펜트는 본래 마법이 담긴 초목이 급성장하며 나타납니다.
column4: Wupent sebenarnya berasal dari beras ajaib yang didapat dari tumbuhan yang tumbuh dengan cepat.

column2: When the demons found glizardons, they immediately subjugated them into minions. Glizardons that aren't minions are still dangerous to humans.
column3: 마족들은 글리자돈을 발견한 후 재빨리 길들여 자신들의 수하로 삼았습니다. 마족이 지배하지 않는 글리자돈 역시 인간에게는 위험합니다.
column4: Saat demon menemukan glizardons, mereka langsung membuatnya menjadi pasukan. Glizardons biasa pun cukup berbahaya bagi manusia.

column2: The Corylus is a mutant hybrid between plants, animals and minerals.
column3: 산호가 변이되어 동식물과 광물의 특징이 공존하는 몬스터입니다.
column4: Corylus adalah monster yang hidup bersama tumbuhan, hewan dan juga mineral.

column2: The reduction in size isn't the only thing that got better after this beast mutated.
column3: 이 야수의 변이후 나아진 점은 크기가 줄어들었다는 점밖에 없습니다.
column4: Monster ini menjadi lebih kuat setelah ukuran tubuhnya berkurang.

column2: It is simple and effective for Beeteros to camouflage. Please do not touch the swaying leaf as it can stab you.
column3: 비테로스들의 위장은 간단하지만 효과적입니다. 공연히 움직이는 나뭇잎을 만지려 하지 마십시오 찔립니다.
column4: Beeteros berkamuflase dengan simpel dan efektif. Jangan sentuh bagian berbentuk daun karena bisa melukaimu.

column2: A mutated mantis. It has gotten stronger and has developed the ability to camouflage.
column3: 사마귀가 변이된 몬스터로 더 강해지고 위장능력이 발전하였습니다.
column4: Monster yang bermutasi dari mantis dan menjadi lebih kuat,  dan memiliki kemampuan menyamar yang baik.

column2: Egnomes carry a stern look. The more stern it looks, the more powerful it is.
column3: 요노움보다 훨씬 엄한 인상을 가지고 있습니다. 더 엄한 만큼 더 강력합니다.
column4: Egnome terlihat sangat menyeramkan. Semakin menyeramkan, maka semakin kuat.

column2: After mutating, Beetow has developed an unreasonable and venomous nature. Its aggression has also become more significant.
column3: 비토우는 변이후 독성과 무리짓는 성질은 사라졌지만, 공격성은 더 커졌습니다.
column4: Setelah Beetow berubah sifat suka berkerumun dan beracunnya menghilang, tetapi menjadi lebih agresif.

column2: Sister of Pawnd. It carries a sickle larger than its own body.
column3: 폰드의 자매로 자신의 몸보다 큰 낫을 들고다닙니다.
column4: Berkeliling membawa sabit yang  lebih besar dari tubuhnya.

column2: Carcashu is a fungus. Its toxins are strong, but there are parts of it that can be eaten.
column3: 카르카슈는 버섯계의 복어입니다. 독성이 강하지만 먹을 수 있는 부분도 있습니다.
column4: Caracashu merupakan jenis ikan keturunan fugu yang beracun, namun ada beberapa bagian yang dapat dimakan.

column2: The Black Maize looks deceptively delicious, eating one will certainly poison you.
column3: 마이즈의 열매는 먹음직스러워 보입니다. 물론 먹으면 중독됩니다.
column4: Biji Buah maize terlihat sangat lezat. Kamu akan ketagihan setelah memakannya.

column2: This monster was bred by the demons and is known for its poisonous abilities.
column3: 마족의 영향을 받아 탄생한 이 몬스터는 민첩하고 독성이 있다고 알려졌습니다.
column4: Monster ini lahir dibawah pengaruh Demon, dan dikenal sangat beracun

column2: Please don't assume that Lapasape can only be encountered in the deep forest, as it sometimes prowls outside to eat human crops.
column3: 깊은 숲속에서만 마주칠 것이라 생각하지 마십시오. 가끔 인간의 작물을 먹기 위해 어슬렁거릴 때도 있습니다.
column4: Tidak hanya ditemui di dalam hutan. Tapi juga berkeliaran untuk memakan hasil panen milik manusia.

column2: Its appearance did not change much, but its physicality has. Lives near water.
column3: 외모는 크게 변하지 않았으나 체질은 완전히 달라진 몬스터입니다. 이제는 물가에만 살지 않습니다.
column4: Penampilan luarnya tidak berubah banyak, namun dari keahliannya menunjukkan dia adalah monster yang sangat berbahaya.

column2: This monster was once the size of a little finger, but it has since grown greatly.
column3: 본래 크기에 비해 가장 덩치가 커진 몬스터입니다. 원래는 새끼 손가락 크기였으니까요.
column4: Monster yang tubuhnya berubah lebih besar daripada sebelumnya, tetapi memiliki jari yang kecil

column2: This monster has evolved from a bird and has since lost its ability to fly.
column3: 몬스터로 변형된 후 날지 못하게 된 새가 많이 있습니다.
column4: Setelah berubah menjadi monster, banyak burung yang tidak dapat terbang.

column2: The Dumaro is a newly discovered monster, which developed its toxic abilities after the Great Plant Cataclysm.
column3: 듀마로는 새로 나타난 몬스터는 아니지만, 초목 폭주의 재앙 이후 독성을 가진 동물이 되었습니다.
column4: Dumaro bukan monster tipe baru, tetapi adalah binatang yang memiliki racun setelah ledakan bencana pada tanaman.

column2: The Lichenclops doesn't only have good eye sight, their sense of smell is also exceptional.
column3: 눈도 조심해야 하지만, 실은 후각도 뛰어납니다.
column4: Kau harus hati - hati terhadap penglihatan dan juga indra penciumannya.

column2: Infroblood is a case where plant spores transform into monsters. It can float.
column3: 식물 포자가 몬스터로 변형된 경우이며 때문에 부유형입니다.
column4: Tanaman berspora yang telah berubah menjadi monster.

column2: Ticen wanders around with a spear, it tends to group with other Ticen variants.
column3: 티켄이 들고다니는 창으로 보아 다른 종류의 티켄이 존재할 수도 있습니다.
column4: Jika melihat akan tombak yang dibawa berkeliling oleh Ticen,mungkin saja terdapat beberapa jenis Ticen lainnya juga.

column2: A tip of Tucen's tail is made out of minerals.
column4: Ujung ekornya memiliki kandungan mineral tertentu.

column2: Since it retains its memory before deformation, this monster has grudges against the people who felled it.
column3: 몬스터로 변형전의 기억을 지니고 있기에 벌목꾼들을 미워합니다.
column4: Dia membenci semuanya karena suatu ingatan di masa lalu sebelum bermutasi.

column2: Although this monster looks small, it has already reached its adulthood. So it might only grow just a bit more.
column3: 작다고는 하지만 이미 성체입니다. 물론 이후에도 계속 성장은 합니다.
column4: Walau tubuhnya kecil, sebenar nya dia sudah dalam tahap dewasa. Dan masih terus bertumbuh.

column2: The Woodfung is closely related to witchcraft.
column3: 우드펑은 주술과 밀접한 관계가 있다고 합니다.
column4: Woodfung katanya sangat berhubungan dengan hal mistis.

column2: They exhibit a unique hull that is a mix between stone and iron.
column3: 이들은 모두 단단한 외피를 지녔지만, 특히 이들은 석질과 철질의 혼합입니다.
column4: Mereka memiliki kulit yang keras seperti batu, terutama mereka itu adalah campuran dari struktur batu dan logam.

column2: It is speculated whether this underground spirit has been deformed and corrupted.
column3: 지하의 정령이 변형되거나 타락한 존재가 아닌가 추측됩니다.
column4: Konon ia yang hidup dibawah tanah telah berubah menjadi hantu dan jahat.

column2: It has been said that Helgasercle was made by the servants of the demon realm's aristocrats.
column3: 마계의 귀족들을 섬기는 하인으로 헬가 세르클이 만들었다고 전해집니다.
column4: Helgacercle diketahui membuatnya untuk melayani para bangsawan dunia demon.

column2: Consumed HP/SP/Stamina can be recovered through the following options.
column3: 소모된 HP/SP/스태미나는 아래 기능을 통해 회복할 수 있습니다.
column4: HP/SP/Stamina yang terpakai dapat dipulihkan dengan beberapa fitur dibawah.

column2: Spontaneous Recovery is slow compared to other recovery methods, but it does not require the player to do anything.
column3: 자연회복은 다른 회복 방법에 비해 매우 느리게 회복되지만 별도의 조작이나 조건이 필요하지 않습니다.
column4: Natural Recovery memiliki efek sangat kecil dibandingkan metode pemulihan lainnya, namun kamu tidak membutuhkan apapun untuk itu.

column2: [Potion Recovery]: Recover HP/SP/Stamina immediately using potions.
column3: [포션회복] : 사용한 포션에 따라 HP/SP/스태미나를 즉시 회복시켜 줍니다.
column4: [Potion Recovery] : Memulihkan HP/SP/Stamina secara instan tergantung potion yang digunakan.

column2: Potions have a cooldown timer before they can be re-used.
column3: 포션 사용 시 재사용 대기시간이 있습니다.
column4: Potions memiliki waktu cooldown sebelum pemakaian berikutnya.

column2: [Tree Root Crystal]: Destroy Tree Root Crystals to recover Stamina.
column3: [나무뿌리 수정 파괴] : 나무뿌리 수정을 파괴하면 스태미나가 회복됩니다.
column4: [Tree Root Crystal Destruction] : Jika menghancurkan Tree Root Crystals maka stamina akan pulih.

column2: {memo }Tree Root Crystals randomly appear in the fields.
column3: 나무뿌리 수정은 필드 곳곳에 무작위로 생성됩니다.
column4: Tree Root Crystal tumbuh secara acak pada semua field.

column2: [Rest Mode]: Using the bonfire during Rest Mode speeds up your recovery.
column3: [휴식모드 활용] : 휴식모드에서 모닥불을 추가로 사용하면 더 빠르게 회복할 수 있습니다.
column4: [Rest Mode] : Gunakan bonfire saat Rest Mode untuk mempercepat efek pemulihan.

column2: Recovery during Rest Mode is faster than Spontaneous Recovery, and it is even faster if you use a bonfire during Rest Mode.
column3: 휴식모드시 자연회복보다 더 빠르게 회복되지만 모닥불을 키면 더 빠르게 회복됩니다.
column4: Daya pemulihan dalam Rest mode lebih cepat daripada pemulihan biasa apalagi jika menggunakan bonfire selama Rest mode.

column2: Overkill will be activated if you kill the monster with a strong finish.

column4: Jika kamu menghancurkan Tree Root Crystals, Stamina dari player disekitar akan ikut bertambah

column2: Some particular skills may overheat when used over a certain number of times.
column3: 특정 스킬은 일정 횟수 이상 연속으로 사용하면 오버히트가 발동합니다.

column2: If Overheat is triggered, that skill goes on cool-down and you will be unable to use it for a while.
column3: 오버히트가 발동되면 해당스킬에 쿨타임이 생기고 잠시 동안 사용할 수 없습니다.
column4: Jika Overheat terjadi, skill tersebut akan memasuki cooldown dan tidak bisa digunakan beberapa saat.

column2: To prevent skills from overheating, you can alternate between using power attacks and basic attacks.
column3: 오버히트가 발생하지 않도록 사용가능한 스킬들을 혼용하면 강력한 공격을 쏟아부을 수 있습니다.
column4: Kamu bisa mengkombinasikan skill dan serangan normal agar tidak terjadi overheat.

column2: Overheat can be suppressed to use many skills.
column3: 다 수의 스킬을 사용하여 오버히트 발생을 억제할 수 있다.
column4: Overheat bisa dicegah dengan menggunakan berbagai macam skill.

column2: Once overheated, you won't be able to use the affected skill for a while.
column3: 오버히트가 발동하면 일정 시간 동안 해당 스킬을 사용할 수 없습니다.
column4: Saat terkena overheat, kamu tidak akan bisa menggunakan skill yang bersangkutan untuk sementara waktu.

column2: The used number of relevant skill will be initialize after a while.
column3: 일정 시간이 지나면 해당 스킬의 사용 횟수가 다시 초기화 됩니다.

column4: Special food dapat diberikan ke Companion-mu untuk memulihkan saat staminanya habis.

column4: Special food untuk Companion dapat dibeli dari Companion Merchant.

column2: Dungeons are very dangerous, but there are special rewards waiting for you.
column3: 던전은 매우 위험하지만 특별한 보상이 기다리고 있습니다.
column4: Dungeons sangat berbahaya, tapi ada hadiah spesial yang menunggumu.

column2: Monsters found in dungeons will attack characters on sight.{nl}Gather more players to form a party and face the challenge!
column3: 던전에 등장하는 몬스터들은 캐릭터를 발견하면 먼저 공격해 옵니다.{nl}파티원을 모집해서 도전해 보세요!
column4: Monster yang muncul di Dungeon akan langsung menyerang target yang terlihat.{nl}Kumpulkan player lain untuk membentuk party dan hadapi tantangannya!

column4: Saat Karakter mati di dalam dungeon, pilih

column3: 을 선택하면 던전 입구로 이동합니다.{nl}던전 깊숙히 들어왔다면 항상 조심하세요!
column4: untuk kembali ke pintu masuk Dungeon. {nl} Berhati-hatilah saat kamu berada cukup jauh di dalam Dungeon!

column2: Gems can be obtained by hunting monsters and bosses in dungeons. {nl} Be careful, as the gems may be lost when you die.
column3: 젬은 던전 몬스터와 보스 몬스터를 사냥해서 구할 수 있습니다{nl}캐릭터가 죽으면 때때로 젬을 잃어버릴 수 있습니다. 조심하세요
column4: Gems bisa didapatkan dari monster pada Dungeon atau Boss pada Dungeon. {nl} Gems bisa terjatuh saat kamu mati. Waspadalah.
Membuat item lain dengan menggabungkan beberapa item

column2: A gem that can be found in a dungeon. {nl}It is able to enhance equipment by equipping it in a socket. {nl}When charged it exerts a stronger power. Right-click to equip it to an equipment.
column3: 던전에서 발견되는 보석입니다. 소켓에 장착하여 장비를 강화할 수 있으며, 마력을 충전하면 더 큰 힘을 발휘합니다. 마우스 오른쪽 클릭 후, 원하는 장비를 선택하여 장착합니다.
column4: Gem dapat ditemukan di dungeon. {nl}Gem dapat meningkatkan kemampuan equipment dengan memasang nya ke dalam slot equip. {nl}Klik kanan untuk memasangnya pada equip yang diinginkan.

column2: Creating weapons in this field require one to have both the skills of blacksmith and farrier. Creating even a simple claw is difficult because of this.
column3: 이 분야의 장비들은 대장장이와 장제사의 재능이 모두 요구됩니다. 그런 점에서 간단한 클로라도 제조가 단순하지 않습니다.
column4: Untuk membuat senjata di bidang ini, seseorang membutuhkan skill seorang Blacksmith dan Farrier. Bahkan untuk membuat Claw sederhana pun akan sulit.

column2: Some devilish beasts are sensitive to iron, and the secrets to manufacturing it are within this recipe.
column3: 마성을 지닌 몇몇 야수는 철에 민감하므로 제조에 비법이 관련됩니다.
column4: Beberapa jenis monster lemah terhadap Attribute Iron, dan rahasianya terdapat dalam resep ini.

column2: It's created using stronger, more resilient iron. The rest is the same as an Iron Claw.
column3: 조금 더 내구력이 강한 쇠로 만듭니다. 그외에는 아이언 클로와 비슷합니다.
column4: Terbuat dari besi yang lebih kuat dan tahan lama. Selebihnya sama dengan Iron Claw.

column2: Created after Medzio Diena to combat plant monsters.
column3: 신수의 날 이후 식물몬스터의 퇴치를 기원하는 뜻이 담겨 있습니다.
column4: Terbuat saat Divine Day, untuk melawan monster tipe Plant.

column2: This claw's original recipe was lost, but it has been recreated by archaeologists who discovered it near Gateway of the Great King.
column3: 이 클로의 제조법은 실전되었다가 대왕의 관문 일대의 고고학자들에 의해 재발견된 후 다시 만들어지고 있습니다.
column4: Resep asli dari Claw ini sudah hilang, tetapi dibuat kembali oleh para arkeolog yang menemukannya di dekat Gateway of The Great King.

column2: It helps when you lose a tooth.
column3: 이가 빠진 경우에도 물 수 있도록 도와줍니다.
column4: Sangat berguna ketika kamu kehilangan gigi.

column2: This kind of item was originally made for pieces.
column3: 이 종류의 아이템은 본래 낱개로도 쓰일 수 있도록 만들어졌습니다.
column4: Sebenarnya item ini dibuat untuk for dipotong.

column2: This tooth was designed to be used only by the valiant.
column4: Gigi ini di desain untuk digunakan oleh pemberani

column3: 입이 아닌 곳에 사용하지 않도록 하십시오.

column2: It's obvious that the owner of these is very confident.
column3: 주인의 신뢰를 받고 있다는 확실한 증거로 볼 수 있습니다.
column4: Sudah jelas bahwa pemilik dari Item ini sangat percaya diri.

column2: Despite using lightweight materials, these claws perform surprisingly well.
column3: 더 가벼운 소재를 사용했지만, 성능을 위해 무게는 유지되었습니다.
column4: Walau terbuat dari bahan yang ringan, Claw ini di luar dugaan berfungsi dengan sangat baik

column2: Some people say it's only good for keeping warm, but that's not true.
column3: 보온용이라 생각하는 사람도 있지만, 사실이 아닙니다.
column4: Sebagian orang mengatakan bahwa Item ini hanya bagus untuk menghangatkan diri, tetapi sebenarnya tidak demikian.

column2: The potential for upgrading durability and performance is better than normal coats.
column3: 보통 코트에 비해 내구력과 성능 향상 가능성이 높습니다.
column4: Kesempatan untuk meningkatkan daya tahan dan penampilan lebih baik dari Coat normal.

column2: There's a rumor that crews use it for sails - it's just as tough.
column3: 질겨서 선원들이 돛으로 쓰인다는 말이 있을 정도입니다.
column4: Rumor mengatakan bahwa beberapa kru menggunakannya saat berlayar - cukup kuat.

column2: Some say you're actually taming the leather.
column3: 몬스터 가죽을 길들인 몬스터에게 씌우는 일도 있다고 합니다.
column4: Sebagian mengatakan bahwa sebenarnya kulitnya yang kau jinakkan.

column2: This saddle can contain all the goods you need, but it's not very comfortable.
column3: 안장과 일체형인 제품이 있지만 그리 편안하진 않습니다.
column4: Saddle ini dapat menampung semua perlengkapan yang kau butuhkan, tetapi agak tidak nyaman.

column2: Companions need training not to swallow the links of all the loose chains.
column3: 고리가 끊어질 경우 떨어진 고리를 삼키지 않도록 길들여야 합니다.
column4: Companion harus dididik untuk tidak memakan rangkaian rantai yang terlepas.

column2: It can be fixed without unpacking.
column3: 파손시 전체를 풀고 다시 엮을 필요 없이 수리가 가능하다고 합니다.

column2: There needs to be consideration about ventilation when mounted on bushy types.
column3: 털이 너무 많은 종류에 착용시 통풍에 신경을 쓸 필요가 있습니다.
column4: Butuh pertimbangan mengenai sistem ventilasi saat menunggangi mount yang berbulu lebat.

column2: There is no noise of shaking vinyl even when moving quickly.
column3: 빨리 움직여도 비늘 떨리는 소리는 나지 않습니다.
column4: Tidak ada suara dari vynil yang bergetar ketika bergerak dengan cepat.

column2: An armor made of surprisingly inexpensive materials.
column3: 의외로 저렴한 소재로 만들어진 아머도 존재합니다.
column4: Armor yang terbuat dari bahan yang ternyata tidak mahal harganya.

column2: It's made so it won't obstruct sight or movement.
column3: 시야와 움직임에 방해가 되지 않도록 착용시키십시오
column4: Dibuat agar tidak mengganggu penglihatan dan pergerakan.

column4: {S18} {#001100} Hancurkan Tree Root Crystal untuk memulihkan stamina. {/}

column4: {S18} {#001100} Kamu dapat mengaktifkan quest dengan menekan Space di sekitar area bendera merah dari NPC. {/}

column2: {s18}{#001100}You can increase various of stats by collecting items for a collection. {/}
column3: {s18}{#001100}콜렉션에 아이템을 모아 능력치를 올릴 수 있습니다.{/}
column4: {S18} {#001100} Kamu dapat meningkatkan kapasitas dengan mengumpulkan item untuk Collection. {/}

column2: Swordsmen are warriors who have strong physical abilities.{nl}They use various weapons to deal with enemies up close{nl}and stand at the front lines.
column3: 소드맨은 강한 맷집과 다양한 무기를 이용해 가까이 몰려든 적을 상대하는 전사입니다.
column4: Swordsman adalah petarung dengan kemampuan fisik yang kuat. Mereka menggunakan berbagai jenis senjata untuk menghadapai musuh di garis depan.

column2: Highlanders are tough fighters who use two-handed swords. They make enemies collide against each other or against terrain, so they are great for handling multiple enemies.
column3: 하이랜더는 양손검을 사용하는 강인한 전사입니다. 적을 다른 적이나 지형에 충돌시킬 수 있어 다수의 적을 상대하기에 유리합니다.
column4: Highlanders petarung handal yang menggunakan two-handed swords. Mereka membuat musuh saling bertabrakan sehingga cocok untuk menghadapi banyak musuh.

column2: Peltastas are defensive warriors who use shields to block enemy attacks and provoke enemies.
column3: 펠타스타는 방패를 사용해 적의 공격을 막아내거나, 적을 도발하여 유인하는 방어형 전사입니다.
column4: Peltastas petarung tipe bertahan yang menggunakan shield untuk menahan serangan musuh dan memprovokasi musuh.

column2: Hoplites use spears with a long attack range. They gain a bonus when fighting against strong, large-sized enemies.
column3: 창을 사용하는 하플라이트는 사정거리가 길고, 중형급 이상의 크고 강한 적을 상대할 때 보너스를 획득합니다.
column4: Hoplites menggunakan Spear untuk jarak jauh. Mereka sangat handal dalam menghadapi musuh berukuran besar dan kuat.

column2: Centurions command the battle with formations. They control their allies and use different formations depending on the situation.
column3: 진영을 갖춘 뒤 전투를 지휘하는 클래스
column4: Centurion memimpin pertarungan dengan formasi khusus.

column2: Barbarians are reckless and aggressive warriors who are not bound to the rules of battle, and would do anything to ensure victory.
column3: 승리를 위해선 형식에 구애받지 않고 무엇이든 하는 바바리안은 저돌적이고 호전적인 전사입니다.
column4: Barbarians adalah petarung yang berani dan agresif. Mereka tidak terikat oleh strategi dan akan melakukan segala cara agar menang dalam pertarungan.

column2: Cataphracts use two-handed spears. They act as cavalry who break through and scatter enemy formations.
column3: 양손창을 전문적으로 사용하는 캐터프랙트는 적들의 방어선을 돌파하여 분쇄시키는 기병 클래스입니다.
column4: Cataphract menggunakan two handed spears. Mereka adalah ksatria berkuda untuk menembus dan mencerai-beraikan formasi musuh.

column2: Rodeleros ambush and demolish enemies. Their defensive skills using shields are effective for blocking long range attacks.
column3: 로델레로는 적을 기습하여 와해시키는 전투의 전문가입니다. 방패를 이용한 방어기술은 원거리 공격을 막아내는데 효과적입니다.
column4: Rodeleros menjebak dan menghancurkan musuh. Skill bertahan mereka dengan menggunakan shield, efektif untuk menahan serangan dari jarak jauh.

column2: Wizards use magic to block attacks and protect themselves.{nl}They can cast powerful and concentrated spells, dealing damage to a single target or multiple enemies in an area.
column3: 마법을 사용하여 상대의 공격을 저지하거나 자신을 보호하는 위저드는 광역 공격을 하는 클래스로, 하나의 대상에 강력한 공격을 퍼붓거나, 다수의 적에게 광역 공격을 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Wizard menggunakan magic untuk menahan serangan atau melindungi diri. Mereka dapat melakukan serangan yang kuat dan terfokus pada satu target maupun serangan magic area terhadap banyak musuh.

column2: Pyromancers use successive hitting fire magic to fight against multiple enemies.
column3: 불을 다루는 파이로맨서는 강력한 화염 지속 마법을 사용하여 다수의 적을 제압합니다.
column4: Pyromancers menggunakan magic berelemen api secara terus - menerus untuk musuh yang berjumlah banyak.

column2: Cryomancers use powerful ice magic to freeze enemies, or protect their allies from enemies by using ice walls.
column3: 빙한을 다루는 크리오맨서는 강력한 마법으로 적을 얼리거나 얼음 장벽으로 적을 가둬 동료을 보조합니다.
column4: Cryomancer menggunakan magic berlemen es untuk membekukan musuh dan melindungi rekan-rekannya dengan menggunakan Ice Wall.

column2: Psychokinos use psychokinesis to control gravity, or pull enemies and throw them around.
column3: 사이코 키노는 염동력을 사용하여 중력을 조작할 수도 있고 적을 끌어당기거나 던져버릴 수 있습니다.
column4: Psychokinos menggunakan psychokinesis untuk mengendalikan gravitasi, mereka dapat menarik dan melempar musuh.

column2: Sorcerers summon and control spirits to fight enemies, or even to use as mounts.
column4: Sorcerer dapat memanggil devils dan mengendalikannya.

column2: Linkers link allies together to reduce the damage they receive, or connect enemies to amplify the damage inflicted.
column3: 링커는 동료을 서로 연결하여 받는 피해량을 줄이거나, 적군을 묶어서 적에게 주는 피해량을 증폭시킬 수 있습니다.
column4: Linker menghubungkan sesama teman untuk mengurangi damage yang diterima atau menghubungkan musuh untuk meningkatkan damage.

column2: Necromancers are wizards who utilize magic involving the dead. They attack with, or create summoned creatures, using corpses collected over time.
column4: Necromancer mengumpulkan dan menggunakan bagian dari mayat monsters.

column2: Thaumaturges use magic that change the attributes and sizes of targets. They can shrink enemies or strengthen allies to aid them in battle.
column3: 쏘마터지는 대상의 속성과 형태를 변화시키는 마법을 구사합니다. 적을 작게 변형시키거나 동료의 신체를 강화시켜 전투에 도움을 줍니다.
column4: Thaumaturges menggunakan magic yang merubah Attribute and ukuran musuh. Mereka dapat melemahkan musuh atau memperkuat teman dalam pertempuran.

column2: Elementalists harness the elements and can cast powerful magic attacks. However, their spells have a long cooldown time, so it is recommended to cooperate with other players.
column3: 엘리멘탈리스트는 원소의 힘을 다루는 마법사입니다. 강력한 공격 마법을 갖고 있지만 스킬을 재사용하기까지 시간이 필요하므로 동료와의 협력이 중요합니다
column4: Elementalist menggunakan magic dengan berbagai elemen untuk menghasilkan serangan yang kuat. Akan tetapi, skill mereka memiliki jeda waktu yang cukup lama sehingga sangat penting untuk bekerja sama dengan yang lain.

column2: Archers use bows and various secondary equipment.{nl}Their specialties are long-ranged and agile attacks.
column3: 아처는 활과 다양한 보조 장비를 활용하여 원거리 전투와 이동 공격에 강한 클래스 입니다.
column4: Archer menggunakan Bow, Crossbow dan berbagai perlengkapan tambahan lainnya . Kemampuan mereka adalah serangan jarak jauh dan menyerang sambil bergerak.

column2: Hunters are trainers who hunt enemies using companions. Companions use skills which require cooperation with their owners, such as biting and holding onto enemies, or finding hidden targets.
column3: 헌터는 컴패니언에게 명령을 내려 적을 사냥하는 조련 클래스입니다. 목표물을 물고 늘어지거나 숨어있는 적을 찾아내는 등 주인과 협력하여 사냥하는 기술을 사용합니다.
column4: Hunter memburu musuh dengan companion-nya. Companion menggunakan skill yang membutuhkan kerjasama dengan pemiliknya dalam melemahkan musuh atau mencari target yang tersembunyi.

column2: Quarrel Shooters use a crossbow and shield for strategic combat. They can defend against long-range attacks using their pavises, placing them in the ground.
column3: 방패와 쇠뇌를 사용하는 쿼렐슈터는 엄폐물을 사용하여 전략적인 플레이를 하는 클래스로, 적의 원거리 공격을 방어하는 동시에 쇠뇌 기술로 접근하는 적을 처리할 수 있습니다.
column4: Quarrel Shooter menggunakan Shield dan Crossbow untuk bertarung dengan strategi. Mereka dapat bertahan dari serangan jarak jauh dan menggunakan catapult skill untuk menghadang musuh yang datang.

column2: Rangers specialize in fighting against multiple enemies with their quick and long-range attacks.
column3: 레인저는 활을 사용하여 원거리에서 빠른 사격을 하는 클래스로 다수의 적을 상대하는데 특화되어 있습니다.
column4: Ranger adalah spesialis dalam melawan musuh yang berjumlah banyak dengan serangan jarak jauh yang cepat.

column2: Sappers are archers who build traps and lure enemies into them.
column3: 새퍼는 덫을 설치하는 궁수로 적군을 자신의 트랩으로 유인하여 공격하는 클래스 입니다.
column4: Sapper adalah pemanah yang memasang trap dan memancing musuh ke area trap.

column2: A Wugushi specialize in using various poisons to attack or bewitch enemies.
column3: 독을 전문적으로 사용하는 무고사는 비전의 방법으로 만든 여러가지 고독을 사용해 적을 공격하거나 고혹하게 합니다.
column4: Wugushi handal dalam menggunakan berbagai macam racun untuk menyerang atau memperdaya musuh-musuhnya.

column2: Scouts specialize in reconnaissance and infiltration. They use stealth to hide themselves and convey the enemy's situation to allies, providing an advantage in battle.
column3: 정찰과 침투에 특화된 스카우트는 자신의 모습을 숨길 수 있고 주변의 상황을 동료에게 전달하여 전투를 유리하게 이끌 수 있습니다.
column4: Scout ahli dalam mengintai dan penyelundupan. Mereka menggunakan Stealth untuk bersembunyi dan memberitahu situasi musuh kepada teman untuk unggul pertarungan.

column2: Clerics heal and protect allies through the blessings{nl}of the goddess, while knocking down their enemies {nl}with powerful blows.
column3: 클레릭은 여신의 은총으로 동료에게는 치유와 보호 마법을, 적군에게는 강력한 타격을 줍니다.
column4: Cleric menyembuhkan dan melindungi teman-temannya dengan berkat para Goddess, sambil mengalahkan musuh dengan serangan yang kuat.

column2: Priests are clerics who give blessings and resurrect the dead with their holy powers.
column3: 프리스트는 성물을 사용하여 동료에게 축복을 내리고 성스러운 힘으로 죽은 이를 부활 시키는 성직자 클래스 입니다.
column4: Priest adalah seorang Cleric yang mampu memberikan berkat and menghidupkan yang mati menggunakan kekuatan suci mereka.

column2: Krivis are priests who use divine fire to help allies recover or to deal massive damage to enemies.
column3: 불을 섬기는 사제인 크리비는 성스러운 불을 사용하여 동료의 회복을 돕거나 적에게 강력한 피해를 입힙니다.
column4: Krivis adalah Priest yang menggunakan api suci untuk memulihkan teman dan memberikan damage besar terhadap musuh.

column2: Bokors use voodoo skills to raise the dead or curse their enemies to attack them from afar.
column3: 부두술의 사제인 보코르는 죽은 사체를 되살려 좀비로 만들거나 적에게 저주를 걸어 멀리서 괴롭힐 수 있습니다.
column4: Bokor menggunakan sihir untuk membangkitkan mayat menjadi zombie atau memberikan curse terhadap musuh.

column2: A Sadhu can use their soul to assault enemies with unseen attacks or convey their powers to other players.
column3: 사두는 자신의 영혼을 유체화하여 적의 눈에 보이지 않게 활동하거나, 자신의 힘을 동료에게 전송할 수 있습니다.
column4: Sadhu dapat melepas jiwanya untuk menyerang musuh atau memberikan informasi keahlian musuh ke sesama rekan.

column2: Dievdirbys can carve and place sacred statues. Their statues can protect allies or attack enemies.
column3: 딥디르비는 성스러운 조각상을 깎아 배치합니다. 이 조각상들은 동료을 보호하거나 적을 공격합니다.
column4: Dievdirby memahat dan meletakkan patung suci untuk melindungi teman atau menyerang musuh.

column2: Monks are clerics who train in martial arts through the blessing of the goddess.
column3: 신체 단련을 통한 수련으로 여신의 은총을 더해가는 성직자입니다.
column4: Monk adalah Cleric yang berlatih seni bela diri dengan mendapatkan berkat dari Goddess.

column2: Pardoners are clerics who don't shy from increasing their wealth through the goddess' blessing.
column3: 여신의 권능이 재물에도 있음을 부정하지 않는 성직자입니다.
column4: Pardoner adalah Cleric meningkatkan kemakmuran mereka melalui berkat para Goddess.

column2: Paladins use their holy power to protect allies and vanquish enemies through the blessings of the goddess.
column3: 강력한 전투력을 발휘하는 팔라딘은 성스러운 힘으로 주변의 동료들을 보호하거나 마신을 숭배하던 적을 개종시켜 여신을 위해 싸우게 합니다.
column4: Paladin menggunakan kekuatan suci untuk melindungi teman dan mengalahkan musuh menggunakan berkat para Goddess.

column2: Lots of Revelators are traveling various collapsed places in the world to look for the arrangement of the goddesses. While they were doing so, they found a place that looks to be the sanctum at Scattered Stairway. If you could recover and use it, you will be the hero to the ones who travel to that region.
column3: 많은 계시자들이 여신의 안배를 찾기 위해 망해버린 세계 곳곳을 모험하고 있습니다. 그러던 중 흩어진 계단에서 성소로 보이는 장소를 찾아냈습니다. 이것을 복구하여 사용할 수 있다면 그 지역을 여행하는 이야기꾼들에게 영웅이 될 것입니다.
column4: Savior bepergian ke seluruh penjuru dunia untuk mencari arrangement of the Goddess. Dalam perjalanan mereka, mereka menemukan sebuah tempat yang tampak seperti sanctum di Scattered Stairways. Jika kamu dapat menemukan dan menggunakan tempat itu kamu akan menjadi hero bagi mereka yang pergi ke sana.

column2: According to what Scouts reported, they found the magical device that they didn't see before at the hillside of Purple Tree Fault Forest. They tried to activate it, but since there are too many monsters nearby, they just fled away. Someone should try activating it and see what effects there will be.
column3: 정찰꾼들의 보고에 따르면 적갈나무 단층숲의 고지대에서 예전엔 보지 못했던 마력장치를 발견했다고 합니다. 활성화해보려고 하였으나 주변의 몬스터들이 너무 많아서 목숨만 겨우 건져서 도망쳐 왔다고 합니다. 누군가 마력장치를 작동시켜서 어떤 효과를 발휘하는지 확인해 봐야 합니다.
column4: Menurut laporan scout, mereka menemukan magical device yang belum pernah mereka lihat sebelumnya di lembah Purple Tree Fault Forest. Mereka mencoba mengaktifkan benda itu, tetapi mereka tidak dapat melakukannya karena dikelilingi oleh monster. Harus ada yang mencoba mengaktifkan benda tersebut dan melihat apa yang akan terjadi.

column2: There is news that Gilliam, a big merchant who did not sell items to anyone, has been placed at the crossroad of a new city.
column3: 아무에게나 물건을 팔지 않기로 유명한 대상 길리엄이 최근 가식의 교차로에서 자리를 잡았다는 소식이 들어왔습니다. 그러나 그곳은 인적이 드물고 사람들이 다니지 않아서 대상 길리엄은 자신을 보호해줄 사람들을 모집하고 있다고 합니다. 만약 대상 길리엄에게 도움을 준다면 그가 판매하는 진귀한 물건을 구입할 수 있을 겁니다.
column4: Terdengar kabar bahwa Gilliam yang merupakan pedagang hebat dan tidak menjual barang kepada sembarang orang, telah mendapat tempat di persimpangan baru. Tetapi di tempat itu orang jalan berlalu lalang, sehingga ia sedang melakukan perekrutan orang-orang untuk melindungi dirinya. Jika memberikan bantuan kepada Giliam, maka dapat membeli item rare yang dijual olehnya.

column4: Seorang gadis pemimpin Mercenary Guild. {nl}Dia diselamatkan saat evakuasi, dan ia adalah anggota dari Mercenary Guild.{nl}Dia bangga atas status Mercenary.

column2: The First Bishop of the St. Ignatius Cathedral, he reformed the church himself by cleansing its false past.{nl}After his death, he continues to be remembered, with the St. Ignatius Cathedral bearing his name.
column3: 사이비교의 역사를 정리하여 그를 바탕으로 교회 자체개혁론을 주장한 성인, 성 이그나티우스 대성당의 초초대 주교, 사후 그의 업적을 기려 성 이그나티우스로 시성되었다.
column4: Seorang Bishop yang diakui oleh Church karena membersihkan Pseudo's History. First Bishop of Ignatius Cathedral, ia memilih Ignatius untuk pengakuan pencapaiannya.

column2: As the goddess who brings the break of dawn, she is called many names.{nl}The Goddess of Dawn. The Daughter of God. The representative of all goddesses.{nl}Carrying out the divine will, she looked after a tree. After she was kidnapped by the Demon Gods, the tree lost control and devoured the capital of the human world.
column3: 주신, 날마다 아침이 밝아오게 만들어주는 여신으로 새벽의 여신이라고도 불리운다. 신의 딸. 모든 여신들의 대표자. 신의 뜻을 이어, 나무를 관리하고 있다. 그녀가 마신들에게 납치된 이후, 나무는 폭주하여 인간계의 수도를 집어삼켰다.
column4: Dinysus, ia disebut sebagai seorang Deity of the Dawn untuk membawa mentari pagi. Daughter of Goddess. Wakil dari semua Goddess. Ia bertanggungjawab atas para Goddess. Furious Trees menguasai dunia manusia, setelah dirasuki Demon Master.

column2: The Goddess of Fate. She can see a thousand years into the future, and prepare accordingly to alter the course of destiny.{nl}She left the Revelators a revelation every 100 years. It is said collecting all the scattered revelations will grant one the power to confront fate.
column3: 운명의 여신. 미리 천 년 후의 미래를 내다보고, 운명을 바꾸기 위해 준비를 해왔다. 100년에 한 번씩 선택 받은 자를 통하여 계시를 남겨두었다. 누군가가 그 흩어진 계시를 모두 모으면, 운명에 맞설 힘을 얻을 것이다.
column4: Fortune. Ia telah meramal ribuan tahun ke depan dan mempersiapkan perubahan takdir. Meninggalkan sebuah wahyu lewat orang-orang terpilih setiap 100 tahun. Kekuatan untuk melawan takdir akan didapatkan, bila seseorang mengumpulkan Scattered Revelation.

column2: Press Enter to open the chat window and press Enter again to close it.
column3: 엔터키를 눌러 채팅 입력창을 열 수 있습니다. 채팅이 끝난 뒤 엔터키를 다시 눌러 채팅 입력창을 닫을 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan Enter untuk membuka Chat Window. Setelah selesai Chat, tekan Enter lagi untuk menutup Window.

column2: Entering /y before your chat allows you to broadcast your message. Requires the Megaphone item.
column3: 채팅창에 /y 를 먼저 쓰면 월드 전체에 메세지를 전할 수 있습니다. 확성기 아이템이 필요합니다.
column4: Ketik /y sebelum chat untuk melakukan Shout ke semua. Kamu membutuhkan Megaphone untuk melakukannya.

column2: You can repair equipment with low durability through the Blacksmith NPC located in a city.
column3: 도시에 있는 대장장이를 통해 내구도가 떨어진 장비 아이템을 수리할 수 있습니다.
column4: Kamu dapat Repair Equipment saat Durability rendah kepada Blacksmiths yang ada di kota.

column2: You can buy and sell items through the merchants NPCs located in the city.
column3: 도시에 있는 상인들을 통해 아이템을 사거나 팔 수 있습니다.
column4: Kamu dapat menjual dan membeli item pada NPC Merchant di kota.

column2: You can return to the quest NPC immediately by using the Backspace key or by pressing the 'Go Back' button.
column3: 퀘스트 완료 후 백 스페이스키 또는 돌아가기 아이콘을 이용하여 완료 NPC 앞으로 이동할 수 있습니다.
column4: Kembali ke NPC Quest dengan menekan tombol 'Backspace' atau tombol 'Go back'.

column2: You can learn class specific attributes from the Master NPCs. Look for them in each area.
column3: 마스터 NPC에게 직업별 특성을 학습할 수 있습니다. 각 지역에 있는 마스터 NPC를 찾아보세요.
column4: Pelajari Attribute sesuai Class dari Master NPC. Temui Master NPC di tiap Area.

column2: Shiny Monsters can drop items up to more than ten times than normal monsters.
column3: 반짝이는 몬스터는 다른 몬스터보다 열 배 이상 많은 아이템이 나올 수 있습니다.
column4: Shiny Monsters bisa memiliki drop rates 10X lipat dari monster normal.

column2: Various merchants and Master NPCs for classes can be found in a village.
column3: 마을에는 다양한 상인 또는 각 클래스의 마스터 NPC 들이 자리하고 있습니다.
column4: Berbagai Merchant dan Master NPC untuk tiap Class berada di dalam kota.

column2: You can move to other areas through the Statue of Goddess Vakarine.
column3: 바카리네 여신상을 통해 다른 지역으로 이동 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Gunakan Warp untuk berpindah menggunakan Goddess Vakarine Statue.

column2: You can move to other areas using the Warp Scroll if there is no Statue of Goddess Vakarine nearby.
column3: 워프 주문서를 이용하면 주변에 바카리네 여신상이 없어도 다른 지역으로 이동 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Kamu juga bisa berpindah dengan Warp Scroll jika tidak ada Goddess Vakarine Statue disekitar.

column2: During your adventure, you can find hidden treasure chests. Some treasure chests may require keys that match the level of the chest.
column3: 모험을 하다 보면 숨겨진 보물상자를 발견할 수 있습니다. 어떤 보물상자는 그 레벨에 맞는 열쇠가 필요할 수 있습니다.
column4: Selama berpetualang, temukan Treasure Chest tersembunyi. Beberapa Treasure Chest membutuhkan kunci sesuai level.

column2: Press F12 to record gameplay videos.
column3: F12 키를 눌러 게임의 동영상을 저장할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F12 untuk merekam Gameplay Video.

column3: Print Screen 키를 눌러 스크린샷을 저장할 수 있습니다.

column2: Press F1 to view info about your character.
column3: F1 키를 이용하여 캐릭터의 정보를 확인할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F1 untuk melihat Karakter Info.

column2: Press F2 to open your inventory to see the items and silver you own.
column3: F2 키를 이용하여 인벤토리를 열어 소지하고 있는 아이템 및 실버를 확인할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F2 untuk Inventory dan melihat item dan Silver yang dimiliki.

column2: Press F1 to view info about your class, skills, and attributes.
column3: F3 키를 이용하여 클래스와 스킬, 특성 정보를 확인할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F1 untuk melihat info Class, Skills, dan Attribute.

column2: Press F4 to view your cumulative record and progress of gameplay.
column3: F4 키를 이용하여 현재까지 플레이하며 누적된 기록을 확인 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F4 untuk melihat akumulasi Record dan progress dari permainan.

column2: Press F5 to view information on current quests in progress.
column3: F5 키를 이용하여 현재 진행중인 퀘스트 정보를 확인 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F5 untuk melihat informasi Quests yang berjalan.

column2: Press F6 to view your party.
column3: F6 키를 이용하여 파티 정보를 확인할 수 있습니다.

column2: Right-click on another player to send a party request. When a request is accepted, you can play together in a party.
column3: 타 캐릭터에 마우스 오른쪽 키를 눌러 파티 초대를 할 수 있습니다. 초대 받은 유저가 수락하면 파티를 맺고 같이 플레이할 수 있습니다.
column4: Klik kanan pada player lain untuk Invite Party. Saat undangan diterima, kamu bisa bermain bersama dalam Party.

column2: Click on Public Party List in the party window to view the current parties in the game.
column3: 게임내 생성 되어 있는 파티의 목록을 표기 합니다. 가입하고자 하는 파티목록을 클릭하면 해당 파티에 가입 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Menampilkan List Party di dalam Game. Klik pada List untuk Join Party.

column2: Press F7 to view your Friends List.
column3: F7 키를 누르면 친구 목록 정보를 확인할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F7 untuk melihat Friend List.

column2: Press F8 to register a gesture or a macro. Or both!
column3: F8 키를 눌러 포즈를 취하거나 매크로를 등록할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F8 untuk menggunakan Pose atau Macro.

column2: Press F9 to view info of your companion.
column3: F9 키를 누르면 현재 컴패니언의 상태를 볼 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F9 untuk melihat Status Companion.

column2: Press F10 to view the Help List.
column3: F10 키를 이용하여 도움말 목록을 확인 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan F10 untuk melihat Help List.

column2: You can adopt and train companions through the Companion Trader NPC.
column3: 컴패니언 상인 NPC를 통해 컴패니언을 분양 받거나 성장시킬 수 있습니다.
column4: Latih Companion lewat Companion Merchant NPC.

column2: Right-click on another player to send trade requests.
column3: 다른 유저에 마우스 오른쪽 클릭을 눌러 거래 신청을 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Klik kanan pada player lain untuk Trade.

column2: Press M to view the current area map.
column3: M 키를 이용하여 현재 지역 맵을 확인할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan M untuk melihat Zone Map.

column2: Press N to view the World Map.
column3: N 키를 이용하여 월드 맵을 확인할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan N untuk melihat World Map.

column2: The durability of an equipped item decreases once the character becomes incapable of combat.
column3: 캐릭터가 전투불능 상태가 되면 착용중인 장비아이템의 내구도가 감소합니다.
column4: Saat Durability Equipment yang dipakai berkurang, kemampuan bertarung bisa berkurang.

column2: Upon reaching a class level of 15, you may advance to the same class or an entire new class.
column3: 전직할 수 있는 클래스 레벨까지 도달하게 되면, 다른 클래스 또는 현재와 같은 클래스로 다시 전직할 수 있습니다.
column4: Saat kamu mencapai Max Class Level, kamu bisa melakukan Advance Class yang sama atau ke Class lain.

column2: Visit the Mercenary Post in Fedimian to take on special missions.
column3: 용병 의뢰소에서 구입한 미션 아이템을 사용하면 포탈을 열어 미션에 입장할 수 있습니다.
column4: Gunakan Mision Item yang diperoleh dari Mercenary Commision untuk membuka Portal dan masuk Mision.

column2: A field boss can sometimes appear in certain areas.
column3: 일부 지역에선 때때로 필드 보스가 등장할 수 있습니다.
column4: Field Boss terkadang muncul di Area tertentu.

column2: Monsters have 1 of the 6 elemental properties: Fire, Ice, Earth, Dark, Poison, or Lightning.
column3: 몬스터는 불, 얼음, 땅, 암흑, 독, 전기의 6가지 속성중 하나씩 고유 속성을 지니고 있습니다.
column4: Monsters memiliki salah satu dari 6 tipe Element: Fire, Ice, Earth, Darkness, Poison or Lightning.

column2: Attacking with countering properties on monsters can cause more damage.
column3: 각 몬스터의 속성에 상응하는 공격시 추가 대미지를 입힐 수 있습니다.
column4: Menyerang dengan elemen kelemahan Monster dapat memberikan Bonus Damage.

column2: Press and hold the attack button to continuously attack a targeted enemy. You can also move while attacking using the arrow keys.
column3: 공격버튼을 누르고 있으면 타겟된 적을 계속 공격할 수 있으며, 이 때 방향키를 이용하여 이동할 수 있습니다.
column4: Tekan dan tahan tombol untuk menyerang musuh terus menerus. Kamu juga dapat menyerang sambil bergerak.

column2: The attacks of the Archer has a maximum range. Higher damage can be dealt when shooting from afar.
column3: 궁수의 활 공격은 최대 사정거리가 존재하며, 멀리서 공격할 때 높은 대미지를 입힐 수 있습니다.
column4: Serangan Arrow dari Archer memiliki jarak maksimum. Semakin jauh jarak maka Damage semakin besar.

column2: Accuracy and evasion increases when an Archer-type class gains a level.
column3: 궁수계 클래스는 레벨업시 명중과 회피가 항샹됩니다.
column4: Accuracy dan Evasion Archer meningkat setiap Class Level naik.

column2: An Archer's basic attack can cause more damage to Flying-type monsters.
column3: 궁수의 기본 원거리 공격은 비행형 몬스터에게 추가 대미지를 입힙니다.
column4: Basic Attack dari Archer memberikan Additional Damage ke Flying Monster.

column2: When a Wizard-type class is attacked during skill casting, the skill can be canceled.
column3: 마법사계 클래스는 스킬 캐스팅중 공격받으면 스킬이 취소될 수 있습니다.
column4: Jika Wizard mendapat serangan saat Casting skill, maka Casting Skill akan gagal.

column2: Magic defense increases when a Wizard-type class gains a level.
column3: 마법사계 클래스는 레벨업시 마법 방어력이 향상됩니다.
column4: Magic Defense dari Wizard meningkat setiap Class Level naik.

column2: Physical defense increases when a Swordsman-type class gains a level.
column3: 전사계 클래스는 레벨업시 물리 방어력이 향상됩니다.
column4: Physical Defense dari Class Swordsman meningkat setiap Class Level naik.

column2: The placed magic circles on the ground from a Cleric-type class may not be effective on Flying-type monsters.
column3: 성직자가 지면에 설치한 마법진은 비행형 몬스터에게 통하지 않을 수 있습니다.
column4: Cleric's Magic Circles terpasang pada tanah dan tidak berefek pada Flying Monsters.

column2: SP and SP recovery rate increases when a Cleric-type class gains a level.
column3: 성직자계 클래스는 레벨업시 SP와 SP 회복량이 향상됩니다.
column4: HP dan SP Recovery Cleric meningkat saat Class Level naik.

column2: Press the CTRL key to lock a target.
column3: Ctrl 키를 누르고 있는동안 타겟이 고정됩니다.
column4: Tekan tombol Ctrl untuk mengunci target.

column2: Press the Alt key to stop movement immediately.
column3: Alt 키를 누르면 이동 중 즉시 멈출수 있습니다.
column4: Gunakan tombol Alt untuk menghentikan gerakan karakter.

column2: Press the Space bar key during a battle to face your current target.
column3: 전투중 스페이스바 키를 누르면 현재 타겟을 바라봅니다.
column4: Tekan Spacebar saat Battle untuk menghadap ke arah musuh.

column2: Your character's stats increases in proportion to the companion's stats when mounting it.
column3: 컴패니언 탑승 시 컴패니언의 능력치에 비례하여 캐릭터의 능력치가 상승합니다
column4: Saat menggunakan Companion, Stat karakter akan meningkat seiring Ability companion.

column4: Apinya terlihat akan padam.{nl}Dapatkan kayu dari monster agar api tetap menyala.

column4: Gunakan Status Points yang kamu dapatkan saat naik level untuk memperkuat Karaktermu.

column2: According to rumors around Fedimian, when the pilgrims passed by the Pilgrim Path
column3: 페디미안 근교에 떠도는 소문으로는 순례자들이 필그림 들길을 순례할때
column4: Menurut rumor di sekitar Fedimian, ketika para peziarah melewati Pilgrim Path

column2: According to the survivors, survivors of the Fallen City lost their belongings or their lives in the Altar Way while going to Fedimian.
column3: 폐도에서 살아남은 자들이 이곳 페디미안으로 향하는 길에 제단로에서 목숨을 잃거나 가진 것들을 모두 빼앗기고 있다고 합니다. 생존자들이 말한 바로는
column4: Menurut para Survivor, Korban selamat dari Fallen City kehilangan barang-barang mereka atau nyawa mereka di Altar pada saat pergi ke Fedimian

column2: Revelators are exploring the different fallen parts of the world to find assignments of the goddess. What seems to be a sanctuary was found in the Altar Way. If you can find something restore and use it again, you will be a hero to those who travel this area.
column3: 많은 계시자들이 여신의 안배를 찾기 위해 망해버린 세계 곳곳을 모험하고 있습니다. 그러던 중 제단로에서 성소로 보이는 장소를 찾아냈습니다. 이것을 복구하여 사용할 수 있다면 그 지역을 여행하는 이야기꾼들에게 영웅이 될 것입니다.
column4: Savior mengeksplor berbagai bagian bumi yang hancur untuk menemukan tugas dari para Goddess. Tempat perlindungan ditemukan di Altar Way. Jika kamu bisa menemukan untuk dihidupkan atau digunakan kembali, kamu akan menjadi pahlawan bagi mereka yang berkelana di daerah ini.

column2: According to the scout's reports, there were spell devices found in the Forest of Prayer. They tried to activate it but there were too many monsters around so they had to run for their lives. Someone has to activate the spell device and check what powers it has.
column3: 정찰꾼들의 보고에 따르면 기원의 숲의 고지대에서 예전엔 보지 못했던 마력장치를 발견했다고 합니다. 활성화해보려고 하였으나 주변의 몬스터들이 너무 많아서 목숨만 겨우 건져서 도망쳐 왔다고 합니다. 누군가 마력장치를 작동시켜서 어떤 효과를 발휘하는지 확인해 봐야 합니다.
column4: Menurut laporan scout, ada spell device ditemukan di Forest of Prayer. Mereka mencoba untuk mengaktifkannya tapi ada banyak monster di sekitar jadi mereka harus menyelamatkan diri. Seseorang harus mengaktifkannya dan lihat kekuatan apa yang ada di dalamnya.

column2: Highlanders are tough fighters who use two-handed swords. They make enemies collide against each other or against terrain, so they are great for handling multiple enemies.
column3: 하이랜더는 양손검을 사용하는 강인한 전사입니다. 적을 다른 적이나 지형에 충돌시킬 수 있어 다수의 적을 상대하기에 유리합니다.
column4: Highlanders adalah petarung tangguh yang menggunakan two-handed swords. mereka membuat musuh bertubrukan satu sama lain atau dengan tanah, mereka sangat hebat mengatasi musuh yang banyak.

column2: Centurions command the battle with formations. They control their allies and use different formations depending on the situation.
column3: 센츄리온 클래스는 포메이션을 사용해 전투를 지휘하는 클래스입니다. 상황에 따라 여러가지 진형을 사용해 동료들을 지휘합니다.
column4: Centurion menggunakan formasi di tiap pertarungan. mereka mengatur prajurit lain untuk menggunakan berbagai macam formasi tergantung situasi.

column2: Corsairs are specialized in dual-wielding and ambushing enemies from behind. Anyone who joins a Corsair's party becomes a pirate.
column3: 커세어는 자신의 파티를 해적단으로 조직하여 독특한 전술을 사용합니다. 적의 아이템을 약탈하거나 보물상자의 획득, 콤보시스템의 사용이 가능합니다.
column4: Corsairs dapat membuat party menjadi pirate group dan bisa menggunakan taktik yang unik. mereka bisa mencuri item musuh, mendapatkan treasure chests, dan menggunakan combo system.

column2: Doppelsoeldners are mercenaries who endure high risk for high rewards. They dangerously expose themselves to enemies to receive high attack power or high EXP.
column3: 도펠죌트너는 많은 보상을 위해 높은 리스크를 감수하는 용병 클래스입니다. 스스로를 위험에 노출시키는 대신 공격력을 높이거나 많은 경험치를 획득합니다.
column4: Doppeldoeldners adalah mercenaries yang bisa menahan resiko tinggi untuk hadiah besar. mereka sangat berbahaya karena mengekspose diri mereka ke musuh dan mendapatkan attack power tinggi atau exp yang besar.

column2: Squires are warriors who support their allies. They support by repairing and enhancing others' weapons, or by setting up a base camp to aid their team.
column3: 스콰이어는 동료를 보조하는 전사계 클래스입니다. 동료의 장비를 손질하여 성능을 향상시키거나 거점을 설치해 동료들의 활동을 도와줍니다.
column4: Squires adalah warrior yang mesupport sesama prajurit. mereka menyuport dengan memperbaiki dan meperkuat senjata yang lain atau membuat basecamp untuk melindungi team.

column2: Alchemists use alchemy to enhance gems and synthesize or craft items.
column3: 알케미스트는 연금술을 이용하여 젬을 강화하거나 아이템의 합성 또는 제작을 할 수 있습니다.
column4: Alchemists menggunakan alchemy untuk memperkuat gem dan menyatukan atau membuat items.

column2: Sorcerers summon and control spirits to fight enemies, or even to use as mounts.
column3: 소서러는 악마를 소환하는 마법사입니다. 소환된 악마를 조종하거나 탑승하여 적을 상대합니다.
column4: Sorcerers adalah wizard yang bisa memanggil Monster. mereka dapat mengontrol atau mengendalikan Monster untuk bertarung dengan musuh.

column2: Chronomancers are wizards who control time. They stop, speed up, or change back time to help allies.
column3: 크로노맨서는 시간을 조작하는 마법사입니다. 시간을 빠르게 하거나 멈춰서 동료들을 도울 수도 있고, 이전의 상태로 시간을 되돌릴 수도 있습니다.
column4: Cronomancers adalah wizard yang dapat mengontrol waktu. mereka dapat memberhentikan, mempercepat, atau merubah waktu untuk menolong dalam pertarungan.

column2: Necromancers are wizards who utilize magic involving the dead. They attack with, or create summoned creatures, using corpses collected over time.
column3: 네크로맨서는 사체를 이용한 마법을 사용하는 클래스입니다. 틈틈히 모아둔 사체로 적을 공격하거나 소환물을 만들어 낼 수 있습니다.
column4: Necromancers adalah wizard yang menggunakan bagian dari orang mati. mereka menyerang atau menyumon menggunakan bagian dari orang mati yang mereka dapatkan.

column2: Rogues are combat professionals who will do anything for victory. They're specialized at ambushing enemies from behind using bows and daggers.
column3: 로그는 승리를 위해서는 무엇이든 하는 전투의 프로입니다. 쇠뇌와 단검을 사용하여 적 뒤에서의 기습, 은신한 상태에서의 활 공격 등 기습전투에 강한 클래스입니다.
column4: Rogue adalah petarung professional yang akan melakukan segala hal untuk menang. mereka mempunyai spesialisasi di bidang ambush musuh dari belakang dengan menggunakan catapault dan sword, atau menggunakan panah ketika dalam stealth mode.

column2: Schwarzer Reiters maneuver quickly. They specialize in diverse shooting techniques using a pistol.
column3: 슈바르츠라이터는 빠른 기동력을 가진 기병 클래스입니다. 권총을 사용한 다채로운 이동 사격기술을 주 특기로 합니다.
column4: Schwarzer Reiters bermanuver dengan cepat. mereka ahli dalam teknik menembak yang beragam menggunakan pistol

column2: Fletchers make and use special arrows. Different arrows result in powerful attacks depending on the type of enemy and combat situation.
column3: 플레쳐는 특수한 화살을 제작하고 사용하는 클래스입니다. 다양한 화살들은 적의 종류와 전투의 상황에 따라 강력한 효과를 발휘합니다.
column4: Fletchers membuat dan menggunakan panah spesial. menggunakan berbagai macam panah tergantung dari tipe musuh dan situasi pertarungan.
